    <string-array name="dice_rules">
        <item>Each player rolls two six-sided (d6) dice — one for body, one for action.</item>
        <item>Die 1 is body zones (6 faces). Die 2 is actions (6 faces). Match the on-screen words to your comfort.</item>
        <item>Die 2 (action, d6): Kiss, Lick, Caress, Bite, Whisper, Tease.</item>
        <item>On your turn, roll both dice and perform the action on the body part rolled.</item>
        <item>Take turns rolling. Use the timer if you turned it on in session setup.</item>
        <item>Double roll: if both dice show the same number, you choose any body part and any action (by agreement).</item>
        <item>Keep a consent signal — tap a hand to stop, smile or nod to continue.</item>
        <item>Optional spicy extras appear sometimes — use them if you want.</item>
        <item>The round ends after five turns each (or when you stop).</item>
        <item>Always prioritize fun, consent, and teasing. Stop or skip anything that doesn\'t feel right.</item>
    </string-array>
